page.name: The End?
page.description: After Xan sank into the lava during your last encounter, his insane fury and magical instability caused him to bind with the lava inside his fortress. He has become the mindless terror called the Lava Titan Xan! Only a DragonLord's power can stop him!

properties.complete: Well done, DragonLord! Lava Titan Xan has been defeated and once more you and your dragon have saved countless lives! Somewhere in that gigantic mass of lava and madness was the real Xan. Has be been defeated once and for all...?
